Package main.model.request

Class Suggestion

java.lang.Object
main.model.request.Suggestion
All Implemented Interfaces:
Displayable, Model, Request, Mappable
public class Suggestion extends Object implements Request
The Suggestion class represents a request made by a student to suggest edits or changes related to a camp. It implements the Request interface.
